snippet.title: Evercade - Jaleco Arcade 1 and Gaelco Arcade 2 Announcement Trailer
snippet.description:
MORE ARCADE IS COMING TO EVERCADE!

Two more great collections of classic arcade titles and hidden gems are coming to Evercade. Playable on Handheld and Evercade VS!

Coming July 2022! Find out more below:
Jaleco Arcade 1: https://evercade.co.uk/cartridges/jaleco-arcade-1/
Gaelco Arcade 2: https://evercade.co.uk/cartridges/gaelco-arcade-2/
